474
00:19:50,590 --> 00:19:52,000
she should focus on resting.

475
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:53,810
If you're so desperate for an heir,

476
00:19:53,810 --> 00:19:56,190
perhaps you should look for someone
stronger and healthier.

477
00:19:56,190 --> 00:19:56,950
Nonsense!

478
00:19:58,760 --> 00:19:59,950
How vicious she is.

479
00:19:59,970 --> 00:20:01,860
Not only is she trying to sow discord
between me and Yue Chi,

480
00:20:01,860 --> 00:20:04,030
now she wants to break me and Ling'er too.

481
00:20:04,030 --> 00:20:05,430
Stronger and healthier?

482
00:20:05,840 --> 00:20:06,830
People who practice martial arts

483
00:20:06,830 --> 00:20:08,400
are usually strong and healthy.

484
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:10,860
Is Yunqing talking about herself?

485
00:20:11,080 --> 00:20:13,120
Alas... Looks like Yunqing

486
00:20:13,140 --> 00:20:15,110
