496
00:20:28,430 --> 00:20:29,350
If there's any bond,

497
00:20:29,350 --> 00:20:29,920
it's between them—

498
00:20:29,920 --> 00:20:31,360
that's what made

499
00:20:31,380 --> 00:20:32,030
her life-saving act

500
00:20:32,030 --> 00:20:33,750
happen.

501
00:20:34,750 --> 00:20:37,160
