542
00:22:28,010 --> 00:22:29,640
Look at other bright places.

543
00:22:30,740 --> 00:22:31,880
Don't always trap yourself

544
00:22:31,880 --> 00:22:33,480
where you only see darkness.

545
00:22:33,770 --> 00:22:35,370
