546
00:22:35,790 --> 00:22:37,590
I can accompany you to find them.

547
00:22:40,440 --> 00:22:41,250
So?

548
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:44,640
The direction you've found

549
00:22:44,640 --> 00:22:46,120
is to willingly

550
00:22:47,110 --> 00:22:48,640
