551
00:22:57,370 --> 00:22:59,830
Back then,
before I went to the battlefield,

552
00:23:00,160 --> 00:23:03,590
you said you wanted the people
to live in peace and prosperity.

553
00:23:03,590 --> 00:23:05,160
The people of Former Ning and those now

554
00:23:05,160 --> 00:23:06,160
are no different.

555
00:23:06,570 --> 00:23:07,650
Unfortunately,

556
00:23:08,290 --> 00:23:09,830
he's just a brute.

557
00:23:10,150 --> 00:23:12,410
How could he know
how to be a good emperor?

558
00:23:13,160 --> 00:23:14,870
It's precisely because he comes from
a humble background,

559
00:23:14,870 --> 00:23:16,400
he understands the suffering
of the common people.

560
00:23:16,400 --> 00:23:18,200
The people need such an emperor,

561
00:23:18,430 --> 00:23:20,080
and I'll do everything I can

562
00:23:20,110 --> 00:23:20,910
to assist him.

563
00:23:24,130 --> 00:23:25,250
