yourself to him wholeheartedly,

565
00:23:29,080 --> 00:23:30,420
only to be discarded

566
00:23:31,030 --> 00:23:33,300
when you're no longer useful.

567
00:23:33,930 --> 00:23:34,940
So,

568
00:23:37,480 --> 00:23:38,830
from the very start, you never planned

569
00:23:38,830 --> 00:23:39,960
to stay and see

570
00:23:41,270 --> 00:23:42,550
if he's truly

571
00:23:42,550 --> 00:23:43,960
a ruler worth following,

572
00:23:46,870 --> 00:23:47,830
did you?

573
00:24:06,260 --> 00:24:07,110
[Yongqian Palace]

574
00:24:07,110 --> 00:24:09,330
