575
00:24:10,610 --> 00:24:11,410
How about...

576
00:24:11,440 --> 00:24:12,900
Fengluan Palace?

577
00:24:15,740 --> 00:24:16,780
She hasn't left?

578
00:24:16,810 --> 00:24:17,670
No, she hasn't.

579
00:24:19,140 --> 00:24:19,970
Let's go, let's go.

580
00:24:19,970 --> 00:24:21,200
To Fengluan Palace!

581
00:24:21,230 --> 00:24:21,920
Let's go.

582
00:24:23,120 --> 00:24:23,970
Ling'er!

583
00:24:29,950 --> 00:24:31,080
Great, great.

