00:24:31,260 --> 00:24:32,190
It's quite nice.

585
00:24:32,680 --> 00:24:34,850
All these things have been moved back, huh?

586
00:24:34,850 --> 00:24:35,650
So you finally

587
00:24:35,680 --> 00:24:38,480
don't have to live at your sister's
place anymore?

588
00:24:40,960 --> 00:24:42,310
In a few days, once I've calmed

589
00:24:42,310 --> 00:24:43,920
the Empress Dowager down,

590
00:24:44,350 --> 00:24:46,270
you can bring her into the palace.

591
00:24:47,250 --> 00:24:48,610
No need, no need.

592
00:24:50,510 --> 00:24:51,110
That Yunqing

593
00:24:51,110 --> 00:24:52,310
of yours

594
00:24:52,330 --> 00:24:54,460
keeps coming to see me again and again.

595
00:24:54,890 --> 00:24:56,090
It's quite annoying.

596
00:24:57,500 --> 00:24:58,370
You...

597
00:24:59,480 --> 00:25:00,750
don't like her?

598
00:25:01,420 --> 00:25:02,590
Of course not.

599
00:25:03,640 --> 00:25:04,110
But...

600
00:25:04,160 --> 00:25:05,360
I think Yunqing seems

601
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:07,920
to quite like Your Majesty.

602
00:25:09,940 --> 00:25:12,000
What nonsense are you talking about?

603
00:25:12,140 --> 00:25:13,140
Think about it.

604
00:25:13,160 --> 00:25:14,940
When she looks at me,

605
00:25:15,000 --> 00:25:16,730
what kind of look does she have?

606
00:25:18,980 --> 00:25:20,200
How could she like me?

607
00:25:20,670 --> 00:25:22,870
It's a miracle she hasn't killed me yet.

608
00:25:29,140 --> 00:25:29,940
Really?

609
00:25:30,120 --> 00:25:31,580
Of course.

610
00:25:31,820 --> 00:25:33,120
I assure you,

611
00:25:33,700 --> 00:25:35,890
she absolutely does not like me.

612
00:25:38,880 --> 00:25:39,730
Well then.

613
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:41,640
If that's the case,

614
00:25:41,700 --> 00:25:43,370
I feel much more at ease.

615
00:25:53,730 --> 00:25:55,730
Just thinking about this annoys me.

616
00:25:56,440 --> 00:25:58,240
I already told Yue Chi that I just

617
00:25:58,260 --> 00:26:00,120
wanted her to leave the capital

618
00:26:00,640 --> 00:26:02,240
and that I wouldn't harm her.

619
00:26:02,500 --> 00:26:04,060
And if he's really worried,

620
00:26:04,330 --> 00:26:06,190
he can send guards to protect her.

621
00:26:07,120 --> 00:26:08,200
But your brother

622
00:26:08,400 --> 00:26:09,600
just won't agree.

623
00:26:09,710 --> 00:26:10,500
Every time I think about it,

624
00:26:10,500 --> 00:26:11,340
I get mad.

625
00:26:11,490 --> 00:26:13,120
How have I been treating him?

626
00:26:13,250 --> 00:26:16,510
He's even harboring a princess
from the previous dynasty.

627
00:26:18,130 --> 00:26:19,580
Jingheng,

628
00:26:19,610 --> 00:26:20,790
listen to me.

629
00:26:21,240 --> 00:26:22,350
Although Yunqing is a princess

630
00:26:22,350 --> 00:26:23,880
from the previous dynasty,

631
00:26:23,920 --> 00:26:26,270
don't treat her like a princess.

632
00:26:26,570 --> 00:26:27,450
She

633
00:26:27,610 --> 00:26:28,690
would never

634
00:26:28,720 --> 00:26:29,790
do anything

635
00:26:29,830 --> 00:26:30,680
to your empire

636
00:26:30,680 --> 00:26:31,880
for wealth and glory.

637
00:26:32,610 --> 00:26:33,680
What do you mean by

638
00:26:34,250 --> 00:26:36,180
"don't treat her like a princess?"

639
00:26:36,400 --> 00:26:38,560
You see, she's usually

640
00:26:38,790 --> 00:26:40,370
very approachable

641
00:26:40,390 --> 00:26:42,480
and she's very frugal.

642
00:26:42,560 --> 00:26:43,790
She treats everyone around her

643
00:26:43,790 --> 00:26:44,590
very well,

644
00:26:44,610 --> 00:26:45,680
truly well.

645
00:26:46,270 --> 00:26:48,270
In short, she's a good princess.

646
00:26:50,150 --> 00:26:51,300
Did Jiang Yunqing

647
00:26:51,490 --> 00:26:53,120
save your life?

648
00:26:53,290 --> 00:26:55,220
Why are you praising her like this?

649
00:26:58,240 --> 00:26:59,300
She did save me.

650
00:27:00,160 --> 00:27:00,960
But compared to

651
00:27:00,960 --> 00:27:02,510
the relationship between
my brother and Yunqing,

652
00:27:02,510 --> 00:27:03,640
it's nothing.

653
00:27:03,690 --> 00:27:04,930
They've been close

654
00:27:05,030 --> 00:27:06,480
since childhood,

655
00:27:07,020 --> 00:27:07,990
and later

656
00:27:08,020 --> 00:27:09,290
they got engaged.

657
00:27:10,760 --> 00:27:12,160
She almost became

658
00:27:12,160 --> 00:27:13,270
my sister-in-law.

659
00:27:18,400 --> 00:27:19,540
This princess

660
00:27:20,670 --> 00:27:21,950
looks so miserable.

661
00:27:22,680 --> 00:27:24,920
She doesn't have
an auspicious look at all.

662
00:27:24,920 --> 00:27:25,720
I don't know

663
00:27:25,750 --> 00:27:27,410
what your brother sees in her.

664
00:27:29,110 --> 00:27:30,310
Why are you laughing?

665
00:27:34,640 --> 00:27:36,790
Whether Your Majesty likes her or not,

666
00:27:37,000 --> 00:27:38,650
to my brother, Yunqing

667
00:27:38,790 --> 00:27:40,060
is a treasure,

668
00:27:40,240 --> 00:27:41,880
a lost gem found again.

669
00:27:42,070 --> 00:27:43,030
So my brother

670
00:27:43,030 --> 00:27:45,230
inevitably becomes overly concerned.

671
00:27:46,160 --> 00:27:46,960
You

672
00:27:47,550 --> 00:27:48,550
and Yunqing

673
00:27:48,750 --> 00:27:50,600
are both very important to my brother,

674
00:27:50,600 --> 00:27:52,160
people he wants to protect.

675
00:27:52,640 --> 00:27:53,400
He doesn't want you

676
00:27:53,400 --> 00:27:55,350
to destroy each other

677
00:27:55,350 --> 00:27:57,410
because of some baseless suspicion.

678
00:27:58,040 --> 00:27:59,700
Your Majesty, think about it.

679
00:28:00,070 --> 00:28:01,790
On one side is his long-lost

680
00:28:01,830 --> 00:28:03,000
beloved,

681
00:28:03,590 --> 00:28:05,110
and on the other

682
00:28:05,110 --> 00:28:06,920
is a wise, capable,

683
00:28:07,750 --> 00:28:09,190
and just ruler

684
00:28:09,400 --> 00:28:11,160
who can fulfill his ambitions.

685
00:28:12,160 --> 00:28:13,420
He doesn't dare to risk

686
00:28:13,440 --> 00:28:14,400
either side.

687
00:28:14,680 --> 00:28:15,880
The only thing

688
00:28:15,880 --> 00:28:16,400
he can do

689
00:28:16,400 --> 00:28:17,960
is keep you apart.

690
00:28:19,000 --> 00:28:20,350
Is there

691
00:28:20,480 --> 00:28:21,440
any better way

692
00:28:21,440 --> 00:28:22,480
than this?

693
00:28:30,250 --> 00:28:31,410
Ling'er,

694
00:28:38,030 --> 00:28:39,030
what angers me

695
00:28:39,400 --> 00:28:40,030
is not that

696
00:28:40,070 --> 00:28:40,880
your brother has dealings

697
00:28:40,880 --> 00:28:43,350
with the princess of the previous dynasty,

698
00:28:44,780 --> 00:28:46,180
but the unfairness in it.

699
00:28:48,470 --> 00:28:50,250
I trust your brother...

700
00:28:53,880 --> 00:28:54,960
this much,

701
00:28:55,980 --> 00:28:57,100
yet he always

702
00:28:57,890 --> 00:28:58,830
seems to

703
00:28:58,830 --> 00:29:00,350
keep a distance from me.

704
00:29:00,810 --> 00:29:02,410
I feel his trust in me

705
00:29:11,890 --> 00:29:13,630
is only this much.

706
00:29:18,130 --> 00:29:19,790
Why does this taste so sour?

707
00:29:24,800 --> 00:29:25,710
I'm sorry.

708
00:29:26,110 --> 00:29:27,480
I'll adjust it.

709
00:29:29,130 --> 00:29:30,100
However,

710
00:29:30,160 --> 00:29:31,760
it has quite a unique flavor.

711
00:29:33,200 --> 00:29:35,510
You're not just trying to
comfort me, are you?

712
00:29:35,510 --> 00:29:36,550
I'm not.

713
00:29:37,270 --> 00:29:38,310
I really think

714
00:29:38,310 --> 00:29:39,570
this wine tastes good.

715
00:29:40,030 --> 00:29:40,870
So,

716
00:29:41,110 --> 00:29:42,770
everyone has their own taste.

717
00:29:43,110 --> 00:29:43,870
No matter

718
00:29:44,090 --> 00:29:45,350
how good that princess

719
00:29:45,710 --> 00:29:47,090
of the previous dynasty is

720
00:29:47,090 --> 00:29:48,090
to you

721
00:29:48,870 --> 00:29:49,910
and your brother,

722
00:29:50,460 --> 00:29:51,770
I will never like her.

723
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:27,260
Why didn't you use the main entrance?

724
00:30:28,290 --> 00:30:30,640
If I had used the main entrance,
it would've meant I was coming as the emperor.

725
00:30:30,640 --> 00:30:32,920
You would have to welcome me
late at night,

726
00:30:32,920 --> 00:30:34,710
causing the whole household to be disturbed

727
00:30:34,710 --> 00:30:36,670
with everyone kneeling on the ground.

728
00:30:36,670 --> 00:30:39,200
She might have started
causing trouble again.

729
00:30:39,200 --> 00:30:40,940
Wouldn't that be a hassle for you?

730
00:30:40,940 --> 00:30:42,740
Wouldn't that be a hassle for me?

731
00:30:43,020 --> 00:30:43,740
Here.

732
00:30:44,690 --> 00:30:46,350
A duck from the Imperial Lake.

733
00:30:46,930 --> 00:30:48,890
And the wine brewed by Ling'er.

734
00:30:53,860 --> 00:30:54,650
Here.

735
00:30:58,220 --> 00:30:59,550
I understand

736
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:02,130
how deeply you care for Jiang Yunqing.

737
00:31:02,680 --> 00:31:04,050
And you're afraid that

738
00:31:04,070 --> 00:31:05,880
I might be wary of her background.

739
00:31:05,880 --> 00:31:07,380
So you want to protect her.

740
00:31:08,070 --> 00:31:09,400
Today, I promise you

741
00:31:09,420 --> 00:31:11,140
I will never constrain her

742
00:31:11,240 --> 00:31:12,770
because of her background.

743
00:31:12,950 --> 00:31:13,910
Even if

744
00:31:13,930 --> 00:31:16,130
Jiang Yunqing stays in your residence,

745
00:31:16,330 --> 00:31:18,160
I won't interfere.

746
00:31:18,570 --> 00:31:19,840
But from today on,

747
00:31:20,700 --> 00:31:21,760
I hope there will be

748
00:31:22,270 --> 00:31:23,270
no more secrets

749
00:31:24,700 --> 00:31:25,960
between us.

750
00:31:31,820 --> 00:31:32,860
Take it.

751
00:31:32,970 --> 00:31:34,700
What an interesting way to eat.

752
00:31:43,290 --> 00:31:44,970
Why is this wine so sour?

753
00:31:46,340 --> 00:31:48,540
Your sister once brewed a fine wine

754
00:31:48,560 --> 00:31:49,960
that was highly praised.

755
00:31:50,060 --> 00:31:51,440
She wasn't satisfied with just that

756
00:31:51,440 --> 00:31:53,180
and wants to become a master brewer.

757
00:31:53,180 --> 00:31:54,010
So...

758
00:31:54,490 --> 00:31:55,260
she started

759
00:31:55,280 --> 00:31:56,740
developing new products.

760
00:31:57,040 --> 00:31:58,400
But in fact,

761
00:31:59,040 --> 00:32:00,120
sometimes,

762
00:32:00,140 --> 00:32:01,540
stepping down at the peak

763
00:32:01,740 --> 00:32:03,020
isn't a bad thing.

764
00:32:03,520 --> 00:32:04,520
At the very least,

765
00:32:05,290 --> 00:32:06,590
you get to become

766
00:32:06,620 --> 00:32:07,780
a legend.

767
00:32:09,570 --> 00:32:11,100
This was brewed by Ling'er.

768
00:32:11,260 --> 00:32:12,390
Have a proper taste.

769
00:32:18,450 --> 00:32:19,440
A proper taste?

770
00:32:20,710 --> 00:32:22,240
It's actually pretty good.

771
00:32:23,440 --> 00:32:25,500
That's exactly what I said back then.

772
00:32:26,120 --> 00:32:27,720
You're quite clever.

773
00:32:30,320 --> 00:32:31,440
Could it be that

774
00:32:31,480 --> 00:32:32,840
after being impressed by my talent,

775
00:32:32,840 --> 00:32:34,240
you started thinking everything

776
00:32:34,240 --> 00:32:35,770
about Ling'er is great too?

777
00:32:36,440 --> 00:32:38,250
Have you ever thought that

778
00:32:38,560 --> 00:32:40,930
maybe it was because I like Ling'er

779
00:32:41,320 --> 00:32:43,780
that I consequently find you
agreeable too?

780
00:32:45,320 --> 00:32:47,010
Hypocrite.

781
00:32:49,130 --> 00:32:49,920
Cheers.

782
00:33:01,080 --> 00:33:01,870
It's fine.

783
00:33:02,990 --> 00:33:03,960
I'm leaving.

784
00:33:06,390 --> 00:33:07,190
Be careful.

785
00:33:15,550 --> 00:33:17,750
He came here

786
00:33:18,830 --> 00:33:20,360
just to promise you safety.

787
00:33:22,640 --> 00:33:24,660
Maybe it's because he's newly
ascended the throne

788
00:33:24,660 --> 00:33:26,120
and still has compassion.

789
00:33:27,960 --> 00:33:29,160
Or maybe...

790
00:33:30,030 --> 00:33:31,360
he's really different.

791
00:33:32,960 --> 00:33:34,960
You trust the promise of an emperor?

792
00:33:35,550 --> 00:33:36,350
Fine.

793
00:33:36,720 --> 00:33:37,790
But don't forget,

794
00:33:37,960 --> 00:33:38,350
I'm just

795
00:33:38,350 --> 00:33:40,620
a woman from the previous royal family.
I'm nothing

796
00:33:40,620 --> 00:33:42,480
like the crown prince
from the previous dynasty.

797
00:33:42,480 --> 00:33:44,440
This matter touches the very foundation
of the two dynasties.

798
00:33:44,440 --> 00:33:45,440
Even if Huo Jingheng

799
00:33:45,440 --> 00:33:46,550
is generous and broad-minded,

800
00:33:46,550 --> 00:33:47,270
would the entire court

801
00:33:47,270 --> 00:33:48,480
simply stand by and do nothing?

802
00:33:48,480 --> 00:33:49,720
Only he knows.

803
00:33:50,070 --> 00:33:51,720
It might not alarm the entire court.

804
00:33:51,720 --> 00:33:52,550
Might not?

805
00:33:53,240 --> 00:33:54,640
Even you said "might not."

806
00:33:54,640 --> 00:33:56,100
That means it's possible.

807
00:33:56,160 --> 00:33:57,960
Do you want to risk Shuo's life

808
00:33:58,160 --> 00:33:59,110
just because you

809
00:33:59,160 --> 00:34:00,890
feel a little guilty right now?

810
00:34:07,790 --> 00:34:09,110
Of course not.

811
00:34:15,170 --> 00:34:16,310
Is this the answer you give me

812
00:34:16,310 --> 00:34:17,790
after these past few days?

813
00:34:19,050 --> 00:34:19,690
Sir,

814
00:34:20,230 --> 00:34:20,840
Yue Chi

815
00:34:20,840 --> 00:34:22,400
sometimes leaves home early
and returns late.

816
00:34:22,400 --> 00:34:23,739
When there's a lot of official business,

817
00:34:23,739 --> 00:34:25,790
he even stays overnight in the palace.

818
00:34:25,790 --> 00:34:27,989
It's really difficult for us to use him.

819
00:34:38,550 --> 00:34:39,320
Sir.

820
00:34:43,030 --> 00:34:43,929
Sir.

821
00:34:46,630 --> 00:34:47,400
Sir.

822
00:34:47,699 --> 00:34:48,699
Sir.

823
00:34:58,000 --> 00:34:59,110
Sir.

824
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:04,890
I remember Fengluan Palace

825
00:35:05,970 --> 00:35:08,430
was the palace of the Empress
of Former Ning.

826
00:35:12,560 --> 00:35:14,080
Now, seeing Yue Ling'er

827
00:35:14,100 --> 00:35:15,060
living there,

828
00:35:15,550 --> 00:35:16,750
do you feel comforted

829
00:35:16,850 --> 00:35:18,370
or upset?

830
00:35:18,950 --> 00:35:20,350
Sir, please spare me.

831
00:35:20,670 --> 00:35:22,590
I have followed your orders.

832
00:35:22,710 --> 00:35:24,670
But Huo Jingheng acts unpredictably.

833
00:35:24,670 --> 00:35:27,030
I have deliberately exposed flaws
many times,

834
00:35:27,030 --> 00:35:28,740
yet I just can't provoke him.

835
00:35:28,880 --> 00:35:30,110
He's simply not taking any action.

836
00:35:30,110 --> 00:35:30,920
Alright.

837
00:35:31,300 --> 00:35:32,480
Then stay here

838
00:35:32,720 --> 00:35:34,050
and think of a solution.

839
00:35:37,280 --> 00:35:38,210
Sir.

840
00:35:39,600 --> 00:35:40,590
Sir!

841
00:35:41,480 --> 00:35:42,480
Sir!

842
00:35:56,560 --> 00:35:58,290
What is the Empress Dowager doing?

843
00:35:58,290 --> 00:35:59,650
I will go check on her.

844
00:36:01,860 --> 00:36:03,060
Protect His Majesty!

845
00:36:05,390 --> 00:36:06,790
Chase after that person!

846
00:36:23,320 --> 00:36:27,830
[Jiang Yunshuo, The Crown Prince of the Previous Dynasty.
He was cared for by Yue Chi for many years.]

847
00:36:30,110 --> 00:36:31,650
Yue Chi,

848
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:34,740
you'd better give me an explanation.
